; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/nvme.md

% nvme, common

# List all NVMe devices
sudo nvme list

# Show device information
sudo nvme smart-log <device>

# Secure erase user data on NVMe device
sudo nvme format <__s___ses_> 1 <__r___reset_> <device>
